Analysis

Total Average Distance = 4.83 km Total Average Classic Bike = 2.19 km - 45% Total Average Eletric Bike = 2.64 km - 55% Total Average Casual User = 2.39 km - 49% Total Average Member user = 2.44 km - 51%

The Casual users are expending more time on riding because they are using Classic Bikes So, are there really less Eletric Bikes than Classic Bikes on the road??? so, do we need to invest on buying more Eletric Bikes???

Analysis II

  • For Business Days, we can invite the users to use Eletric Bikes for more commodity and quickly destiny,
  • For weekends, we can invite the users to use Classic Bikes as a healty life way with the family.
